Get Repository Contents

Source: R/repo_contents.R
repo_contents.Rd

Retrieves Github Repository Contents/filenames

repo_contents(repo, ...)

repo_files(repo, ...)

Arguments

repo

Github repository in the order or user/repo
...

arguments passed to gh

Value

A list or a character vector of files

Examples

repo_contents("muschellij2/fslr")
